<th colspan="2" class="summary" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold; background-color: #EEDD82"><a href="Academy_Award" title="Academy Award">Academy Award</a> for Best Director</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left; width:33%;">Awarded for</th>
<td class="" style="">"Excellence in cinematic direction achievement"</td>
