<li>3 &#160;: <a href="Frank_Capra" title="Frank Capra">Frank Capra</a> (6)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Billy_Wilder" title="Billy Wilder">Billy Wilder</a> (8)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="David_Lean" title="David Lean">David Lean</a> (7)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Fred_Zinnemann" title="Fred Zinnemann">Fred Zinnemann</a> (7)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Steven_Spielberg" title="Steven Spielberg">Steven Spielberg</a> (7)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Elia_Kazan" title="Elia Kazan">Elia Kazan</a> (5)</li>
