<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Clint_Eastwood" title="Clint Eastwood">Clint Eastwood</a> (4)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Frank_Lloyd" title="Frank Lloyd">Frank Lloyd</a> (4)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="../Joseph_L._Mankiewicz" title="Joseph L. Mankiewicz">Joseph L. Mankiewicz</a> (4)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Milo%C5%A1_Forman" title="Miloš Forman">Miloš Forman</a> (3)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Leo_McCarey" title="Leo McCarey">Leo McCarey</a> (3)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Lewis_Milestone" title="Lewis Milestone">Lewis Milestone</a> (3)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Oliver_Stone" title="Oliver Stone">Oliver Stone</a> (3)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Robert_Wise" title="Robert Wise">Robert Wise</a> (3)</li>
<li>2 &#160;: <a href="Frank_Borzage" title="Frank Borzage">Frank Borzage</a> (2)</li>
<li>1 &#160;: <a href="Woody_Allen" title="Woody Allen">Woody Allen</a> (7)</li>
<li>1 &#160;: <a href="Martin_Scorsese" title="Martin Scorsese">Martin Scorsese</a> (7)</li>
